equation: T_ext_sin.offset + (if time < T_ext_sin.startTime then 0.0 else T_ext_sin.amplitude * sin(6.283185307179586 * T_ext_sin.freqHz * (time - T_ext_sin.startTime) + T_ext_sin.phase))

T_int_setback.offset + (if time < T_int_setback.startTime or T_int_setback.nperiod == 0 or T_int_setback.nperiod > 0 and T_int_setback.count >= T_int_setback.nperiod then 0.0 else if time < T_int_setback.T_start + T_int_setback.T_width then T_int_setback.amplitude else 0.0)
assert(T_int_setback.period >= 1e-60, "Variable violating min constraint: 1e-60 <= T_int_setback.period, has value: " + String(T_int_setback.period, "g"));
